/www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Anya_Taylor_Joy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/furiosa"><em>《愤怒的麦克斯传奇》</em></a>在戛纳电影节上获得了长达六分钟的起立鼓掌，据报道，这让演员和导演乔治·米勒激动不已。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/furiosa-a-mad-max-saga-review-3756466">《Furiosa：疯狂的麦克斯传奇》评论：另一部强大的、浸透汽油的杰作</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部电影定于 5 月 23 日广泛上映，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anya-taylor-joy">安雅·泰勒-乔伊</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-hemsworth">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯</a>主演，是 2015 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-hardy">汤姆·哈迪</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charlize-theron">查理兹·塞隆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zo-kravitz">佐伊·克拉维茨</a>主演的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/best-film-past-25-years-rotten-tomatoes-3473276"><em>《疯狂的麦克斯：狂暴之路》</em></a>的前传。</p><p>在前传中，泰勒-乔伊饰演年轻版的塞隆，但被残暴的军阀德门图斯（海姆斯沃斯饰）夺走。福瑞奥莎被迫与一大群摩托车手一起穿越荒原，必须奋力寻找回家的路，而德门图斯和同为暴君的不朽乔则为争夺沙漠的统治地位而战。 </p><figure id="attachment_3756486" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3756486" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3756486" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth.jpg" alt="福里奥萨" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Furiosa_Chris_Hemsworth-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3756486" class="wp-caption-text">克里斯·海姆斯沃斯在《疯狂的麦克斯传奇》中饰演德门图斯。图片来源：华纳兄弟。</figcaption></figure><p> <em>《疯狂麦克斯传奇》</em>昨天（5 月 15 日）在戛纳首映，一如法国电影节的传统，观众长时间起立鼓掌。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/festivals/anya-taylor-joy-furiosa-cannes-standing-ovation-mad-max-1235999808/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《综艺》</em></a>报道，海姆斯沃斯在掌声中变得情绪激动，同时他还被拍到亲吻导演乔治·米勒的头部。您可以观看下面的视频。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7AFqY4OSAG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C5